<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>噴塗產線監控系統 UI_V29 Engineer Integrated</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/dashboard.css?v=20260708_v28">
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <div>
            <h1>噴塗產線監控系統</h1>
            <p>SprayingLineMonitoringSystem · UI_V29 Engineer Integrated</p>
        </div>
        <div class="header-meta">
            <div id="updateTime">最後更新時間：--</div>
            <div id="wsHeaderBadge" class="local-badge checking">Webservices 連線檢查中</div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="main">
        <section class="summary">
            <article class="summary-card"><h3>總站數 TotalStations</h3><div class="number" id="totalCount">0</div></article>
            <article class="summary-card"><h3>正常 Normal</h3><div class="number" id="normalCount">0</div></article>
            <article class="summary-card"><h3>注意 Warning</h3><div class="number" id="warningCount">0</div></article>
            <article class="summary-card"><h3>預測風險 PredictRisk</h3><div class="number" id="riskCount">0</div></article>
        </section>

        <section class="source-panel" id="sourceStatus">
            <div class="connection-main">
                <span id="connectionDot" class="connection-dot checking"></span>
                <strong id="connectionTitle">Webservices 連線檢查中...</strong>
            </div>
            <div id="connectionDetail" class="connection-detail">正在確認 UI、Webservices、PostgreSQL 與三個 Service API。</div>
            <button class="connection-refresh" onclick="loadIntegrationStatus()">重新檢查</button>
        </section>
        <section class="station-area" id="stationArea"></section>

        <section class="timeline-panel">
            <div class="timeline-top">
                <div>
                    <h2>單一時間點檢視 TimePointViewer <span id="liveStatusBadge" class="live-badge">即時更新中｜每15秒</span></h2>
                    <p>原本的單點狀態保留；滑動時間軸後，三站卡片會切換到指定的過去、現在或未來時間點。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mode-buttons">
                    <button id="timeModeBtn" class="active" onclick="setMode('time')">時間模式 TimeMode</button>
                    <button id="batchModeBtn" onclick="setMode('batch')">批次模式 BatchMode</button>
                    <button onclick="backToLive()">回到即時 BackToLive</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="time-chips">
                <div class="time-chip" id="pastChip">過去 Past</div>
                <div class="time-chip active" id="nowChip">現在 Now</div>
                <div class="time-chip" id="futureChip">未來 Future</div>
            </div>

            <div class="slider-area">
                <input type="range" id="timeSlider" min="-6" max="4" step="1" value="0" oninput="handleSliderChange()">
                <div class="time-labels time-mode" id="sliderLabels">
                    <span class="left-label">過去6小時</span>
                    <span class="now-label">現在</span>
                    <span class="right-label">未來2小時</span>
                </div>
                <div class="selected-time" id="selectedTimeText">目前時間點：現在</div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-result" id="timelineResult">資料載入中...</div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <script src="/static/trend_chart.js?v=20260708_v28"></script>
    <script src="/static/dashboard.js?v=20260708_v28"></script>
</body>
</html>
